    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/c3dad22fc464beb1bdb00a7d4801ff24.avif?t=1745838361\" width=616 height=384 /></span><br><br>Beautiful Desolation是一款发生在未来的等距视角冒险类游戏。在揭开秘密的旅途中，你能体验末世后的景色、解决谜题、结交新朋友、对抗强敌、调解冲突以及为自己的性命而战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/8f8fb1902d4d55f4c7fc83e5cb08a083.poster.avif?t=1745838361\" width=624 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/8f8fb1902d4d55f4c7fc83e5cb08a083.webm?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/8f8fb1902d4d55f4c7fc83e5cb08a083.mp4?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>THE BROTHERHOOD让你重新体验童年时代冒险游戏的乐趣。Beautiful Desolation是一款发生在未来的等距视角冒险类游戏。在揭开秘密的旅途中，你能体验末世后的景色、解决谜题、结交新朋友、对抗强敌、调解冲突以及为自己的性命而战。<br>宏大的冒险故事<br>游戏中你将扮演超脱时间之人——马克，他来到了遥远的未来，这里的科学技术高度发达，既备受推崇，又遭人唾弃，马克需要找到失散的兄弟唐和回家的路。你的周围回荡着荒凉过去的声音，你的行为将书写尚能窥见的黑暗未来。准备好面临艰难的选择吧，脚下的旅途将影响这方土地。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/b69e300baca8b5e1f3ba5036b063eb61.poster.avif?t=1745838361\" width=624 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/b69e300baca8b5e1f3ba5036b063eb61.webm?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/b69e300baca8b5e1f3ba5036b063eb61.mp4?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这里壮丽的自然景观灵感源于非洲，在探索的旅途中你将遇到形形色色的本土居民，有些会帮助你，有些会为难你。或是与当地的领袖、医师和战士和平协商，或是卷入了纳米群、巨蝎和机器人的战斗之中<br><br><br>繁荣的村庄、破败的城市、石化的森林、干涸的海床，这奇异而崭新的世界为你展现了多种多样的地貌，在2D等距艺术的渲染上更具美感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ca32d6e93d80431609f61331342d2798.poster.avif?t=1745838361\" width=628 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ca32d6e93d80431609f61331342d2798.webm?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ca32d6e93d80431609f61331342d2798.mp4?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>大师谱写的乐章<br><br>Beautiful Desolation中的音乐由Mick Gordon创作，其知名作包括Wolfenstein®，DOOM®, Prey®, Killer Instinct®以及Need for Speed®。<br><br>游戏特色<br>引人入胜的冒险故事，反乌托邦的后末世未来<br>独具魅力的环境<br>简单的操作，深邃的谜题<br>经典的解谜冒险游戏<br>奇异的生物与鲜活的角色<br>丰富多彩的对话以及选择<br>值得探究、前所未见的世界<br>40多名形形色色的角色等待你去结识<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ff960bbcf1adffe955573e6b6cfc93e1.poster.avif?t=1745838361\" width=624 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ff960bbcf1adffe955573e6b6cfc93e1.webm?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912570/extras/ff960bbcf1adffe955573e6b6cfc93e1.mp4?t=1745838361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>评测<br>…游戏中的世界充满创意而又不失美感…<br>极其出色的作品。<br>Beautiful Desolation非常不错。<br><br>值得信赖的精品<br>Beautiful Desolation是The Brotherhood工作室在打造STASIS（2015年度冒险游戏）和CAYNE后推出的又一部精品游戏。",
